          This video is proof of that. We shot it all on an iPhone 6s over the course of a few hours. 
        </p>

        <div class="subslogan">
          And you can do it too.
        </div>

        <p class='emphasize'>
          We’ve created this four-part course to help teach you some skills and tricks to shooting great video on a shoestring budget - and without expensive film equipment or setups. We’ll also provide some of the resources we use to organize and help set up a shoot, so you can start creating great, simple video for your campaigns and marketing efforts.    
        </p>
      </div>
      
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="sign-up-form-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="writeup-container">
        <div class="writeup">
